to continue as a guest. TIDE &amp; POOL accounts are useful for storing address and billing information as well as expediting future shopping experiences on tideandpool.com.\r\n\r\n<strong>26. DOES TIDE &amp; POOL TAKE TELEPHONE ORDERS? Â </strong>\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, at this time we do not take orders by phone. You may only order at tideandpool.com.\r\n\r\n<strong>27. HOW CAN I PURCHASE MORE THAN THREE TOWELS OF THE SAME DESIGN?</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you would like to purchase more than three towels of the same design please contact us at customerservice@tideandpool.com or (562) 277-1382 and we will do our best to accommodate your request.\r\n\r\n<strong>28. WHICH CREDIT CARDS DOES TIDEANDPOOL.COM ACCEPT?</strong>\r\n\r\ntideandpool.com accepts American Express, Visa and MasterCard.Â  Credit cards must have a U.S. billing address.\r\n\r\ntideandpool.com does not currently accept cash, checks or money orders.\r\n\r\n<strong>29. DOES TIDEANDPOOL.COM CHARGE SALES TAX?</strong>\r\n\r\nA 9% sales tax will be applied to the product total on all orders shipped within California. Residents in other states are responsible for complying with the tax laws that apply to online purchases in their respective states.\r\n\r\n<strong>30. HOW DO I RECEIVE WEB PROMOTIONS OR SPECIAL OFFERS?</strong>\r\n\r\nTo be notified about special offers and promotions, please sign up for the TIDE &amp; POOL Swim Club mailing list.Â  Simply sign up by clicking on the â€˜SWIM CLUBâ€™ link within the header of every page on tideandpool.com. Alternatively, you can subscribe to the mailing list by entering your email address in the field located at the bottom of every page.\r\n\r\n\r\nIn order to take advantage of these promotions, please enter the promotional code in the space provided on the â€œOrder Reviewâ€ page and click â€œApplyâ€ before you place your order. The value of the promotion will be applied to your order and appear in the â€œDiscountâ€ field.\r\n\r\n<strong>31. HOW DO I CARE FOR MY TIDE &amp; POOL TOWELS?</strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL towels are designed with enduring quality in mind. With proper care our vibrant designs will be a part of many sunny days to come.\r\nMachine-wash your towel on cold and before first use.\r\nTumble dry your towel at a low temperature.\r\nAvoid using fabric softener. It can reduce your towelâ€™s absorbency.\r\nDo not bleach or dry clean your towel.\r\nOur fiber reactive dyes resist fading caused by chlorine, salt water and exposure to sunlight during regular use. However, please do not store your towels in direct-sunlight.\r\n\r\n<strong>32. WHERE DOES TIDE &amp; POOL MANUFACTURE ITS MERCHANDISE AND IS IT ENVIRONMENTALLY COMPLIANT?</strong>\r\n\r\nTIDE &amp; POOL towels are produced in Brazil, a country known for its stunning coastline, lively beach culture and beautiful textiles. In the textile business for over 120 years, our manufacturer combines a century of craftsmanship with modern innovations in production techniques and sustainable manufacturing. Like TIDE &amp; POOL, they have an ongoing commitment to the responsible use of our natural resources and have been awarded the Fritz Muller Trophy for their environmental management system four times.', 'FAQs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'faqs', '', '', '2013-01-19 21:30:16', '2013-01-19 21:30:16', '', 0, 'http://local.tideandpool.com:8888/?p=411', 21, 'post', '', 0),
